item.title: Yacht club’s Far-Eastern adventure
item.author: Felix Editor,Alex Eckl,Bob Xu,
item.description: From the 27th to 31st of October 2016, the 10th China Cup International Regatta was hosted in Shenzhen, attracting over 140 teams from all over the world including Russia, the USA, Australia and Germany, amongst others. Imperial College Yacht Club (ICYC) sent out Team Imperial, comprised of students …
